videoDetails.Title: The Last Real Tank Destroyer
videoDetails.Description:
Decal link: https://tinyurl.com/42thwzv3

Most modern tank destroyers in War Thunder use missiles to engage targets, but the Chinese PTZ89 is different. It uses a cannon like older TD designs. 

Check the channel "About" section for the link to the creator of my profile picture.
